            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>提醒！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%89%E4%BC%8F%E8%B4%B4%E8%B4%B4%E6%95%B7%E9%97%B4%E9%9A%94%E4%B8%BA10%E5%A4%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%89%E4%BC%8F%E8%B4%B4%E8%B4%B4%E6%95%B7%E9%97%B4%E9%9A%94%E4%B8%BA10%E5%A4%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#三伏贴贴敷间隔为10天#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%B4%B4%E4%B8%89%E4%BC%8F%E8%B4%B4%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%89%E7%82%B9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%B4%B4%E4%B8%89%E4%BC%8F%E8%B4%B4%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%89%E7%82%B9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#贴三伏贴注意三点#</span></a> ：①应忌烟酒和辛辣、生冷、油腻等刺激性食物，以免影响疗效。②三伏贴的贴敷时间是，一般成人贴敷6小时，儿童2—4小时。根据个体差异，贴敷时间也可以做适当调整。③三伏贴不是治疗慢性病的特效药，不能完全替代其他治疗，正在服药的慢性病患者不要盲目减药、停药。戳看哪些人不适合贴👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A604dP3t" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
